## Asset Fingerprinting

Propshaft automatically fingerprints assets in production for cache busting.

### How It Works

```
# Source file
app/assets/images/logo.png

# Development (no fingerprint)
/assets/logo.png

# Production (with fingerprint)
/assets/logo-2f5b3c8a9d1e4f7a6c8b9e0d1f2a3b4c.png
```

### In Views

```erb
<!-- You write: -->
<%= image_tag "logo.png" %>

<!-- Development generates: -->
<img src="/assets/logo.png">

<!-- Production generates: -->
<img src="/assets/logo-2f5b3c8a9d1e4f7a6c8b9e0d1f2a3b4c.png">
```

**Benefits:**
- Browsers cache assets aggressively
- Changing file content changes fingerprint
- No stale cache issues

